data.title: Family Office Exchange
data.text:
Our Community

Community is central to FOX.

We work with families, family office executives, advisors, and industry partners to facilitate peer connection and learning opportunities for every member of the family office profession.

Becoming a member of the FOX community means joining a network of people with decades of combined experience dedicated to continuous learning, peer support, and connection.

Our Services

FOX provides access to resources, knowledge, and connections.

FOX is the premier organization for families and family office professionals. Our vast network and industry leading resources are an essential tool for optimizing your family office.

Consulting, networking, educational events, thought leadership, resource partners, and industry research are just some of the resources we use to ensure that you have everything you need on your, your family's, or your office's journey.
